articles.title: AEW Revolution media scrum notes: Sting talks final match & his future - Figure Four Online
articles.description: Sting talked to the press following his retirement match.
articles.content:
Both Sting and Tony Khan talked to the media following AEW Revolution.
Sting discussed why he chose AEW as his final destination, as well as what he would like to do in the future with the company. … [+3836 chars]
